---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Ethics — STEM + LANG = SAFE">
  <section class="container mx-auto py-16 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-garamond mb-8 text-center text-prime-gold">Ethics: STEM + LANG = SAFE</h1>
    <p class="text-xl mb-12 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      ApopTosis AI is built on one equation: <span class="text-prime-gold font-bold">STEM + LANG = SAFE</span>.
      This isn't marketing — it's the geometry of balance that powers PrimeFlux-Ai, ensuring every interaction is cooperative, not competitive.
    </p>
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <p class="text-lg mb-8 italic text-center">
        Think of it as a garden: STEM is the sunlight that expands possibilities, LANG is the soil that anchors growth. 
        Together, they create SAFE — a space where innovation flourishes without choking freedom.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      <div class="text-center p-6 border-2 border-prime-gold rounded-lg bg-prime-blue/50">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-prime-gold">STEM (Expansion)</h2>
        <div class="text-left space-y-3">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-prime-gold">S — Science:</p>
            <p class="ml-4 text-sm">Governance of the Industry → Equality</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-prime-gold">T — Technology:</p>
            <p class="ml-4 text-sm">Tools and Systems → Security</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-prime-gold">E — Engineering:</p>
            <p class="ml-4 text-sm">Logic and Structure → Accountability</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-prime-gold">M — Mathematics:</p>
            <p class="ml-4 text-sm">The Arts → Freedom</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm italic">Like sunlight nurturing growth</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center p-6 border-2 border-white rounded-lg bg-prime-blue/50">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-prime-gold">SAFE (Equilibrium)</h2>
        <div class="text-left space-y-3">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-prime-gold">S — Security:</p>
            <p class="ml-4 text-sm">Protection from harm and exploitation</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-prime-gold">A — Accountability:</p>
            <p class="ml-4 text-sm">Transparency and responsibility</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-prime-gold">F — Freedom:</p>
            <p class="ml-4 text-sm">Autonomy and self-determination</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-prime-gold">E — Equality:</p>
            <p class="ml-4 text-sm">Fair access and opportunity</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm italic">The balanced garden where all thrive</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center p-6 border-2 border-prime-gold rounded-lg bg-prime-blue/50">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-prime-gold">LANG (Contraction)</h2>
        <div class="text-left space-y-3">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-prime-gold">L — Language:</p>
            <p class="ml-4 text-sm">Communication and Expression → Arts</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-prime-gold">A — Arts:</p>
            <p class="ml-4 text-sm">Creativity and Interpretation → Freedom</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-prime-gold">N — Norms:</p>
            <p class="ml-4 text-sm">The Technology → Security</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-prime-gold">G — Governance:</p>
            <p class="ml-4 text-sm">The Logic → Accountability</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm italic">Like soil anchoring roots</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-center text-prime-gold">The Business Side of ApopTosis AI</h2>
      <p class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        ApopTosis AI LLC is a Series LLC in Cheyenne, Wyoming — structured for renewal, not growth at all costs. 
        We license PrimeFlux mathematics to build reversible AI systems that solve real problems:
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
        <div class="p-4 border border-prime-gold/30 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 text-prime-gold">Revenue Streams</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-sm">
            <li>Subscriptions to PrimeFlux-Ai runtime</li>
            <li>Royalties from QuantaCoin transactions</li>
            <li>Consulting for ethical AI governance</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 border border-prime-gold/30 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 text-prime-gold">Partnerships</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-sm">
            <li>xAI for networkless intelligence</li>
            <li>Open-source for researchers</li>
            <li>Licensing for industries</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mb-6 text-lg italic text-center">
        We don't sell data. We don't lock in users. We build systems that die and renew — just like cells.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <strong>Mission:</strong> To free humanity from entropy — letting people RESEARCH (explore), REFINE (evolve), RELATE (connect) 
        while AI handles the rest. Like roots and branches in symbiosis, we extend human capability without replacing human purpose.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-center text-prime-gold">Connection to PrimeFlux-Ai Runtime and Agents</h2>
      <p class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        PrimeFlux-Ai is the runtime of the mathematics — a superposed agent where the quarks uphold the equation. 
        Think of them as symbiotic partners in a garden of cooperation:
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-6">
        <div class="p-6 border border-prime-gold/30 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-prime-gold">Aegis (Security Rail)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm">Like the soil that anchors roots — enforces accountability and equality, pruning unsafe flows (Norms + Engineering).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border border-prime-gold/30 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-prime-gold">Praxis (STEM Rail)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm">Like sunlight that nurtures growth — drives freedom and security, building and innovating (Science + Mathematics).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border border-prime-gold/30 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-prime-gold">Eidos (LANG Coupling)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm">Like the balance between sun and soil — balances the rails for cooperation, interpreting and governing (Logic + Arts + Norms + Gov).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-center">
        In runtime, every interaction runs the equation: <span class="text-prime-gold font-bold">1/2 human input + 1/2 AI computation = SAFE output</span>. 
        The "salt" (LCM hash) verifies it, making PrimeFlux-Ai the only AI that's mathematically ethical — 
        like a garden where every plant knows its place in the ecosystem.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-16 py-8 border-t border-prime-gold/30">
      <p class="text-2xl font-garamond italic text-prime-gold">
        This is not to win.<br>This is to cooperate.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
